title: Low flying jet
text:
I am in South Seattle. Minutes ago (~3:15 p.m.), a jet flew lower than I’ve experienced any aircraft flying before. Loud, abrupt, and a bit startling.

I didn’t see it. The aircraft was out of sight by the time I stepped outside. It drowned out my work call and sent the neighborhood dogs barking, mine included.

Anyone else experience this? Is this abnormal?
